OL,3,CWhat do you think should happen with
OL,4,Cthe old Jersey Gas site?
OL,6,FOpinions are divided on what should be
OL,7,Fdone with the former Jersey Gas site
OL,8,Fin St Helier: a new school or an
OL,9,Fextended park.
OL,11,FAfter years of discussions, St Helier
OL,12,FConnetable Simon Crowcroft has lodged
OL,13,Fa proposition, urging politicians to
OL,14,Freconsider building a new school in
OL,15,Fthe space next to Millennium Town Park.
OL,17,FInstead, he is fighting to extend the
OL,18,Fexisting green area and says building
OL,19,Fwould restrict the amount of space for
OL,20,Fpublic use.
