OL,3,CWhat do you think should happen with
OL,4,Cthe old Jersey Gas site?
OL,6,FThe Education Minister, Deputy Rob
OL,7,FWard, wants to close St Luke's and
OL,8,FSpringfield schools once this new one
OL,9,Fis up and running.
OL,11,FDefending the current plans, Deputy
OL,12,FWard says: "This also comes with the
OL,13,Fold Springfield site becoming a park
OL,14,Ffor that area, plus Les Bas Centre
OL,15,Fbecoming a green space, so we are
OL,16,Fincreasing those types of areas.
