OL,3,CWhat do you think should happen with
OL,4,Cthe old Jersey Gas site?
OL,6,F"At the moment, those students at St
OL,7,FLuke's and Springfield have no green
OL,8,Fspace to run about in during their
OL,9,Fbreaktimes, so every single day they
OL,10,Fmiss out.
OL,12,F"With a new school, they will have
OL,13,Fthat. This is just as equally
OL,14,Fimportant for them."
OL,16,FDeputy Ward adds: "Staff are having to
OL,17,Fwork miracles every day with the
OL,18,Ffacilities they have. This was agreed
OL,19,Fsome years ago and should be in place
OL,20,Fby now, but we seem to be taking this
OL,21,Ffor debate again.
