OL,3,CWhat do you think should happen with
OL,4,Cthe old Jersey Gas site?
OL,6,F"I just want us to get on with
OL,7,Fbuilding the new school, which has
OL,8,Falways been so needed."
OL,10,FHowever, Connetable Crowcroft says
OL,11,Fthis project would prevent his plan to
OL,12,Fexpand Millennium Town Park.
OL,14,FIn his proposition, he says: "I make
OL,15,Fno bones about wanting the Assembly to
OL,16,Freconsider the decision taken in the
OL,17,FBridging Island Plan... to build a new
OL,18,Fprimary school on the only site which
OL,19,Fcould ever be used to extend the
OL,20,FMillennium Town Park.
