OL,3,CWhat do you think should happen with
OL,4,Cthe old Jersey Gas site?
OL,6,F"I am passionate about parks, and my
OL,7,Fbelief in their environmental, social,
OL,8,Ftherapeutic and economic value to the
OL,9,Fwhole community has only grown since
OL,10,Fthe pandemic."
OL,12,FHe adds: "I am fighting so hard to get
OL,13,Fthe park extended because you can
OL,14,Fbuild a new school, if you need to,
OL,15,Fsomewhere else, but you can't extend
OL,16,Fthe town park anywhere else but here."
OL,18,FThe earliest date politicians will
OL,19,Fdebate Connetable Crowcroft's
OL,20,Fproposition is Tuesday 24 June.
