OL,3,CWhat do you think should happen with
OL,4,Cthe old Jersey Gas site?
OL,6,FSasha Gibb, who founded a local group
OL,7,Fto give the community a voice on how
OL,8,Fpublic space is used, adds: "97% of
OL,9,Fthe kids are Springfield School
OL,10,Falready don't have outdoor green space
OL,11,Fof their own. The park is their
OL,12,Fgreenspace, the park is their school,
OL,13,Fthey are intertwined.
OL,15,F"There is no reason why the solution
OL,16,Fshould not embrace both, a fantastic
OL,17,Fschool and a fantastic park, and I
OL,18,Fknow that we can do that.
